<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 06:11:31 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>美国犹太艺术家对美化哈马斯大屠杀的艺术作品感到愤怒，感到沉默和疏远</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-07-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/u-s-jewish-artists-angered-by-artwork-that-glorifies-hamas-massacre-feel-alienated/00000190-b011-d7ee-af9c-ff1925b20000</link><description>当纽约一个著名的文化空间向一位艺术家展示其橱窗并对哈马斯 10 月 7 日的袭击表示赞赏时，许多犹太和以色列艺术家感到震惊，但并不完全感到惊讶。正如一位策展人所指责的那样，艺术界是否创造了“一个从单一角度看待现实的平坦领域”？</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 05:35:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-07-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/u-s-jewish-artists-angered-by-artwork-that-glorifies-hamas-massacre-feel-alienated/00000190-b011-d7ee-af9c-ff1925b20000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡命令以色列军队在10月7日之后关闭会议录音</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-16/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-ordered-israeli-army-to-turn-off-recording-of-meetings-after-october-7/00000190-b7ef-db47-abb0-bfffd0900000</link><description>通常情况下，录音系统是自动运行的，记录陆军总部指挥中心发生的一切，但战争一开始，总理就下令关闭所有录音。军队遵守了这个命令</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 03:02:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-16/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-ordered-israeli-army-to-turn-off-recording-of-meetings-after-october-7/00000190-b7ef-db47-abb0-bfffd0900000</guid></item><item><title>现在正在加沙作战，10 月 7 日炮击基布兹房屋的以色列国防军军官并不后悔</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-16/ty-article/.premium/now-fighting-in-gaza-idf-officer-who-shelled-a-kibbutz-house-on-october-7-has-no-regrets/00000190-b806-db47-abb0-ba77d8b20000</link><description>10月7日，尼西姆·哈赞上校驾驶一辆受损坦克前往贝埃里基布兹，在那里与哈马斯恐怖分子进行了整整两天的战斗。正是在那里，他向佩西·科恩的家发射了一枚炮弹。他告诉《国土报》，他不知道里面有人质。 “那天我们需要改变现状，”他说</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 03:01:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-16/ty-article/.premium/now-fighting-in-gaza-idf-officer-who-shelled-a-kibbutz-house-on-october-7-has-no-regrets/00000190-b806-db47-abb0-ba77d8b20000</guid></item><item><title>三名以色列人在约旦河西岸的一辆汽车枪击事件中受轻伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-16/ty-article-live/barrage-of-rockets-fired-at-northern-israel-after-three-killed-in-lebanon-airstrike/00000190-b936-db47-abb0-bb77e2b30000</link><description>周一晚间，以色列北部城镇发射了 20 枚火箭弹 ■ 真主党证实，一名真主党成员在以色列发起的 Bint Jbeil 袭击中丧生 ■ 三名以色列人在约旦河西岸枪击事件中受伤 ■ 据报道，Gallant 告诉人质家属，协议“是有史以来最接近的”到过&amp;#39;</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 02:33:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-16/ty-article-live/barrage-of-rockets-fired-at-northern-israel-after-three-killed-in-lebanon-airstrike/00000190-b936-db47-abb0-bb77e2b30000</guid></item><item><title>JD万斯在当选特朗普副总统后首次发表讲话，敦促以色列“尽快”结束加沙战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-16/ty-article/.premium/j-d-vance-trumps-vp-pick-urges-israel-to-finish-gaza-war-as-quick-as-possible/00000190-b947-da51-a19a-fdef7b240000</link><description>这位俄亥俄州参议员曾写道，特朗普可能是“美国的希特勒”，他指责拜登总统“让以色列越来越难赢得这场战争”，并发誓要“重振以色列和沙特阿拉伯之间的和平进程”</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 02:24:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-16/ty-article/.premium/j-d-vance-trumps-vp-pick-urges-israel-to-finish-gaza-war-as-quick-as-possible/00000190-b947-da51-a19a-fdef7b240000</guid></item><item><title>报道：国防部长加兰特告诉人质家属“以色列有史以来最接近达成协议”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-15/ty-article/.premium/israels-defense-minister-this-is-the-closest-we-have-ever-been-to-a-deal/00000190-b7e9-db81-a3f7-f7fda3ae0000</link><description>据以色列第 12 频道援引未透露姓名的消息人士的报道，10 月 7 日，国防部长约阿夫·加兰特在会见在军事基地被绑架的以色列国防军女观察员家属时，暗示与哈马斯的人质谈判取得了重大进展</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 19:58:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-15/ty-article/.premium/israels-defense-minister-this-is-the-closest-we-have-ever-been-to-a-deal/00000190-b7e9-db81-a3f7-f7fda3ae0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列高等法院命令国家解释为什么斯德泰曼拘留设施不依法运作</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-15/ty-article/.premium/israels-top-court-to-state-explain-why-sde-teiman-doesnt-operate-according-to-the-law/00000190-b7b6-db47-abb0-bff71d060000</link><description>该国表示打算将被拘留者转移到以色列其他监狱或将他们送回加沙，但此后一再要求推迟。在该州再次要求推迟后，法官要求政府在 10 天内做出回应</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 19:45:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-15/ty-article/.premium/israels-top-court-to-state-explain-why-sde-teiman-doesnt-operate-according-to-the-law/00000190-b7b6-db47-abb0-bff71d060000</guid></item><item><title>2014年，以色列与哈马斯开战。十年后，我们正经历着残酷的重演</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-07-15/ty-article/.premium/in-2014-israel-went-to-war-with-hamas-ten-years-later-we-are-living-a-grim-replay/00000190-b777-d5a5-af99-ff7794060000</link><description>我们已经用十年的时间从​​ 2014 年发生的事件中汲取教训，其中许多事件似乎预示着即将发生的事情。这一次，没有任何借口让加沙恢复现状——我们已经看到，这对于以色列人和巴勒斯坦人来说是多么不可持续和危险</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 18:43:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-07-15/ty-article/.premium/in-2014-israel-went-to-war-with-hamas-ten-years-later-we-are-living-a-grim-replay/00000190-b777-d5a5-af99-ff7794060000</guid></item><item><title>以色列消息人士称，试图杀死德伊夫损害了与哈马斯的停火谈判</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-15/ty-article/.premium/attempt-to-kill-deif-hurt-cease-fire-negotiations-with-hamas-israeli-sources-say/00000190-b792-db47-abb0-bff3bcd40000</link><description>一位以色列消息人士表示，“事情并没有像往常一样进行。”一位政府消息人士称，“哈马斯遭受了严重打击，他们对这一事件的反应非常软弱，近乎无反应。”结果，摩萨德主任尚未启程前往卡塔尔进行谈判</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 18:39:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-15/ty-article/.premium/attempt-to-kill-deif-hurt-cease-fire-negotiations-with-hamas-israeli-sources-say/00000190-b792-db47-abb0-bff3bcd40000</guid></item><item><title>阿拉伯人和巴勒斯坦人谴责以色列对“安全”区哈马斯指挥官的不作为</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-07-15/ty-article/.premium/arabs-and-palestinians-decry-inaction-over-israel-targeting-hamas-commander-in-safe-zone/00000190-b6a2-d64e-a1d7-f7e677d30000</link><description>在以色列对本应安全的地区进行大规模轰炸后，以色列阿拉伯城市的抗议者集会“声援加沙人民”，而整个阿拉伯世界的许多人则在社交媒体上指责他们的政府缺乏保护。结束战争的努力</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 18:29:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-07-15/ty-article/.premium/arabs-and-palestinians-decry-inaction-over-israel-targeting-hamas-commander-in-safe-zone/00000190-b6a2-d64e-a1d7-f7e677d30000</guid></item><item><title>欧盟制裁以色列极右翼领导人、极端主义定居者团体和前哨基地</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-15/ty-article/.premium/european-union-sanctions-israeli-far-right-leaders-extremist-settler-groups-and-outposts/00000190-b77d-d3a7-a79e-f77f7d000000</link><description>以色列担心，在国际法院就以色列占领西岸是否符合国际法的合法性作出裁决后，对与西岸定居点有关的实体和个人实施的日益严厉的制裁将会加剧</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 18:27:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-15/ty-article/.premium/european-union-sanctions-israeli-far-right-leaders-extremist-settler-groups-and-outposts/00000190-b77d-d3a7-a79e-f77f7d000000</guid></item><item><title>报告：与叙利亚阿萨德有联系的商人在以色列袭击中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-07-15/ty-article/report-businessman-with-ties-to-syrias-assad-killed-in-israeli-attributed-strike/00000190-b795-de8b-adfc-bfb525fa0000</link><description>据报道，与真主党有经济联系、此前曾受到美国制裁的巴拉·卡特吉(Baraa Katerji)在袭击中身亡</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 18:22:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-07-15/ty-article/report-businessman-with-ties-to-syrias-assad-killed-in-israeli-attributed-strike/00000190-b795-de8b-adfc-bfb525fa0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列交战，第 283 天：以色列国防军袭击加沙中部南部；欧盟制裁以色列极右活动人士和实体</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-15/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-283-idf-strikes-gaza-eu-sanctions-far-right-israeli-activists/00000190-b74a-db47-abb0-bf7b65240000</link><description>在哈马斯发表相互矛盾的声明后，以色列官员表示，达成协议的谈判仍在继续。 ■ 以色列国防军袭击加沙南部和中部，试图对哈马斯施加更大压力。 ■ 总理内塔尼亚胡就煽动反对他的问题举行会议后，反对党领袖亚伊尔·拉皮德表示：“内塔尼亚胡不是一个受害者;他是个爱发牢骚的人，也是个胆小鬼。 ■ 欧盟对五名以色列极右活动分子和三个实体实施制裁 ■ 战争进入 283 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 17:09:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-15/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-283-idf-strikes-gaza-eu-sanctions-far-right-israeli-activists/00000190-b74a-db47-abb0-bf7b65240000</guid></item><item><title>亚伊尔·内塔尼亚胡在人质交易关键时刻批评卡塔尔后引发新争议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-15/ty-article/yair-netanyahu-sparks-fresh-controversy-after-criticizing-qatar-at-key-hostage-deal-moment/00000190-b71b-d5a5-af99-ff1b20b40000</link><description>据瓦拉报道，他在迈阿密举行的一次会议上表示，卡塔尔是“仅次于伊朗的世界第二大恐怖主义资助者”，并声称他们资助反以色列校园抗议活动。一名卡塔尔官员驳斥了这些说法，称其为“无稽之谈”，并表示这可能会使人质谈判“复杂化”</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 16:50:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-15/ty-article/yair-netanyahu-sparks-fresh-controversy-after-criticizing-qatar-at-key-hostage-deal-moment/00000190-b71b-d5a5-af99-ff1b20b40000</guid></item><item><title>Wiz 做什么？谷歌将如何从此次收购中受益？这对以色列意味着什么？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-15/ty-article/.premium/what-does-wiz-do-how-will-google-benefit-and-what-does-it-mean-for-israel/00000190-b6f0-d8f7-add0-f7faf2270000</link><description>如果这家以色列网络安全公司确实被美国科技巨头以 230 亿美元收购，这将标志着以色列经济的一个里程碑。它的创始人和员工会赚多少钱，它将如何影响云计算，以及以色列将从销售中获得多少税收？</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 16:29:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-15/ty-article/.premium/what-does-wiz-do-how-will-google-benefit-and-what-does-it-mean-for-israel/00000190-b6f0-d8f7-add0-f7faf2270000</guid></item><item><title>“无犹太复国主义区”：全球旅游景点越来越不受欢迎以色列人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-15/ty-article/.premium/zionist-free-zone-israelis-are-increasingly-unwanted-at-global-tourism-sites/00000190-b60f-d9f4-afd5-fe8fec740000</link><description>从京都的一家酒店到爱丁堡的三明治店，全世界都对以色列人产生敌意，他们了解到假期并不能保护他们免受加沙战争的影响</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 14:58:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-15/ty-article/.premium/zionist-free-zone-israelis-are-increasingly-unwanted-at-global-tourism-sites/00000190-b60f-d9f4-afd5-fe8fec740000</guid></item><item><title>以色列必须允许记者进入加沙自由独立报道</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-07-15/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israel-must-allow-journalists-into-gaza-to-report-freely-and-independently/00000190-b1b6-d3c7-ab94-bfff13050000</link><description>包括《纽约时报》、BBC 和 CNN 在内的 70 多个新闻和民间社会组织签署了一封致以色列的公开信，重申呼吁国际媒体不受限制地进入加沙。持续的限制导致错误信息和虚假信息泛滥</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 14:26:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-07-15/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israel-must-allow-journalists-into-gaza-to-report-freely-and-independently/00000190-b1b6-d3c7-ab94-bfff13050000</guid></item><item><title>加沙边境社区谴责最高安全顾问内塔尼亚胡在 10 月 7 日之后未能访问基布兹</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-15/ty-article/.premium/kibbutz-blasts-netanyahu-top-security-adviser-for-failing-to-visit-community-after-oct-7/00000190-b610-df08-a9fe-f7d0f07a0000</link><description>尼尔奥兹集体农场（Kibbutz Nir ​​Oz）是哈马斯袭击中受灾最严重的社区之一，在国家安全负责人为总理辩护“将一生奉献给加沙边境社区的重建”后，该组织的成员对他进行了猛烈反击。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 13:17:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-15/ty-article/.premium/kibbutz-blasts-netanyahu-top-security-adviser-for-failing-to-visit-community-after-oct-7/00000190-b610-df08-a9fe-f7d0f07a0000</guid></item><item><title>阿莫斯·哈雷尔：“内塔尼亚胡正在利用特朗普枪击事件来诽谤以色列的抗议运动”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-07-15/ty-article-podcast/amos-harel-netanyahu-is-using-the-trump-shooting-to-vilify-israels-protest-movement/00000190-b59a-df08-a9fe-f5dae7f80000</link><description></description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 12:50:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-07-15/ty-article-podcast/amos-harel-netanyahu-is-using-the-trump-shooting-to-vilify-israels-protest-movement/00000190-b59a-df08-a9fe-f5dae7f80000</guid></item><item><title>极右翼极端分子袭击组织者后，耶路撒冷警方拆除了艺术展</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-15/ty-article/.premium/jerusalem-police-takes-down-art-exhibit-after-far-right-extremists-assault-organizers/00000190-b5d3-df08-a9fe-f5d3c4310000</link><description>该展览试图强调自 10 月 7 日以来冲突对儿童的影响。极右极端分子指责组织者“反对以色列国防军士兵”，其中一人破坏了艺术品并袭击了一名组织者</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 11:59:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-15/ty-article/.premium/jerusalem-police-takes-down-art-exhibit-after-far-right-extremists-assault-organizers/00000190-b5d3-df08-a9fe-f5d3c4310000</guid></item></channel></rss>